de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure

Class AbstractUnmodifiableList<DataType,EncapsulatedType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.mrapp.android.adapter.datastructure.AbstractUnmodifiableList<DataType,EncapsulatedType>
  • Type Parameters:
    DataType - The type of the items of the list
    EncapsulatedType - The type of the items of the encapsulated array list
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Unmodifiable, java.lang.Iterable<DataType>, java.util.Collection<DataType>, java.util.List<DataType>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    UnmodifiableGroupList, UnmodifiableItemList, UnmodifiableList

    public abstract class AbstractUnmodifiableList<DataType,EncapsulatedType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<DataType>, Unmodifiable
    An abstract base class for all implementations of the type List, which should throw exceptions of the type UnsupportedOperationException when attempted to be modified. Such a list is intended to encapsulate an other list.
    Since:
    0.1.0
